\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ ||X||_{\text{Tr}}-||\widetilde{C}||_{\text{Tr}}\right\} _{\rho}$
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $d_{A},d_{B}=2,\dots,11.$
\end_inset

 The red cross points out the maximum value.
 For equal dimensions the criteria seems to be equivalent.
 The most relevant difference appear in 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(2,d_{B}\right)$
\end_inset

 where the histogram shifts and the maximum difference presents a local
 minimum as can be visualize in Fig.
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig: sic-d2_11"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

